{"tid":1164530,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"吉利副總裁否認減薪傳言 指今年員工最多加薪30%","createTime":"2019-05-21T07:13:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-21T11:30:56.000Z","uid":117934,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"40a81f6e0d9402522f1ddd723d45bffbfbad16de","tid":1164530,"uid":117934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T07:13:27.000Z","msg":"吉利集團副總裁楊學良於其個人微博中表示，吉利汽車各項經營指標良好，發展穩健，沒有所謂「降薪」情況出現。吉利汽車從5月起正式開展2019年度薪酬調整工作，本次調薪優秀員工薪酬增長最高可達30%。為了讓中高層幹部更有使命感、目標感和結果意識，8崗以上員工自願加入經營結果共擔激勵機制，目標完成回報會更高。<br />\n<br />\n內地網站流傳一張吉利汽車員工自願降薪申請書的相片，列明員工為了共同承擔公司經營，自願下調工資及年終獎金。(ic/t)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YYB8kd5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYYB8kd5.png&h=84354482&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d57f6ce0930a46f50c44ba68ea1623ab46998826","tid":1164530,"uid":254735,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:18:34.000Z","msg":"隻野我24入 仲坐緊"},{"pid":"ca3fb2ea6ae50b21804df9cf03bcfca4c4d65ecd","tid":1164530,"uid":117281,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T09:54:34.000Z","msg":"義工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a0afb3d76ae81ca671a2193a9226eeff01df2f4","tid":1164530,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:05:57.000Z","msg":"本次調薪優秀員工薪酬增長最高可達30%<br />\n<br />\n只限高層？"},{"pid":"10646abff08e188222372161a831a2b15f2ae406","tid":1164530,"uid":94824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:22:56.000Z","msg":"8蚊好快到"},{"pid":"6b8a441fab3fa6a9744a22c4ca05c1b12d2a9ee9","tid":1164530,"uid":73856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:25:54.000Z","msg":"5000 加30% 得1個<br />\n冇講大話架都可以"},{"pid":"9f867a9bddfdd0c139d693ae20fffaf4534d4b53","tid":1164530,"uid":78791,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-21T11:27:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5826aa20b9b7a893f3e4d6ca29708089e3489a84","tid":11